'''蘇格蘭教會'''（{{lang-en|Church of Scotland}}；{{lang-sco|The Scots Kirk}}，常稱 the Kirk ；{{lang-gd|Eaglais na h-Alba}}）或稱'''蘇格蘭長老會'''，是[[蘇格蘭|蘇格蘭]]的一個[[長老宗|長老宗]][[教會|教會]]，是蘇格蘭名義上的國教<ref>[http://www.royal.gov.uk/MonarchUK/QueenandChurch/QueenandChurch.aspx Queen and the Church], royal.gov.uk. Retrieved 5 July 2015. {{Wayback|url=http://www.royal.gov.uk/MonarchUK/QueenandChurch/QueenandChurch.aspx |date=20150707002938 }}</ref>，但並不受國家控制。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://bothwellparishchurch.org.uk/welcome/the-church-of-scotland/|title=Church of Scotland|date=17 February 2011|publisher=|access-date=2018-08-01|archive-date=2021-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210117090037/https://bothwellparishchurch.org.uk/welcome/the-church-of-scotland/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=0HqoVsg6gycC&pg=PA479&lpg=PA479&dq=%22A+national,+but+not+a+state,+church.%22&source=bl&ots=UEmDL2KC14&sig=Slrc-bsPcVXMtLB0FCCmKHw86p4&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwi25JHE96rQAhVpAcAKHSWLDPwQ6AEIHDAA#v=onepage&q=%22A+national,+but+not+a+state,+church.%22&f=false|title=Handbook of European History 1400 - 1600: Late Middle Ages, Renaissance and Reformation|date=14 March 1994|publisher=BRILL|first1=Thomas A.|last1=Brady|first2=Heiko Augustinus|last2=Oberman|first3=James D.|last3=Tracy|via=Google Books}}</ref><ref name="Kirk&State">{{Cite web|url=http://www.churchofscotland.org.uk/about_us/how_we_are_organised|title=How we are organised. The Kirk and the State|accessdate=24 October 2016|work=Church of Scotland website|publisher=Church of Scotland|archive-date=2014-07-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140724211731/http://www.churchofscotland.org.uk/about_us/how_we_are_organised|dead-url=yes}}</ref>苏格兰教会是[[世界归正宗团契|世界归正宗团契]]的一员。<ref name="WCRC2018">{{cite web|url=http://wcrc.ch/members|title=Members|accessdate=15 April 2018|year=2018|publisher=World Communion of Reformed Churches|language=en|archive-date=2015-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/2015123008